name: Colored Dummies
description:
We live a different life in the world of colors and we are very accustomed to colors.
The color of the world is one of the greatest divine gifts that has caused the joy and happiness of human beings and has reached hope and peace in them.
We are all aware of the existence of colors, but are we also aware of their effect on our soul, psyche, mind and thoughts? Colors have miraculous effects on the human soul and psyche, and the interest in certain colors reveals many unspoken things in their minds and souls.
This is my collection entitled Colored Puppets taken from the characters of the childhood world and the effective effect of color on the world of children.
